  <brief_title>Efficacy and Safety of Electrical Versus Pharmacological Cardioversion in Early Atrial Fibrillation</brief_title>
  <official_title>Efficacy and Safety of Electrical Versus Pharmacological Cardioversion in Early Atrial Fibrillation: a Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
